{
  "stem": "20581.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we decided we're gonna put, like, 50 people in a train and send them over to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they put 50 people in a train to go to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough-- I wasn't on that train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody else took these people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure enough, they came to [INAUDIBLE], and they turned them back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came back to Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we're talking to [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Abba Weinstein. ?] He says, look.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought back all the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Abba, ?] you know what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm going to take them across the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Say, yeah?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You want to take 'em?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You're-- they're here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Go ahead, take 'em",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure enough, I tell the people-- you know, we used to work-- we used to make tricks, like-- we used to tell the people, like, listen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you get over on the other side and you get caught by the police, or by the border police, let's say, if you-- when we came, we took the people from Salzburg to [INAUDIBLE], which is Austria to Germany.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got caught in the German side, we used to tell them, I said, listen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you get caught, you tell that the reason you, you were going to smuggle the-- the border, you wanted to go from [INAUDIBLE] to Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you were going to smuggle the-- you were gonna cross the border to Austria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're gonna tell you no good, so you got to go back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then the people who we wanted to bring into Salzburg, we used to tell them, when you get caught, you tell them you wanted to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Say, oh, no good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can't go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You gotta stay in Austria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
